    "- **Price Sensitivity**: High elasticity (-1.2) - highly responsive to price changes\n",
    "- **Time Flexibility**: High (0.8) - very flexible with scheduling\n",
    "- **Strategic Value**: Low importance (1/3) - transactional relationship\n",
    "- **Demand Response**: 30-40% shift to off-peak with 15% discounts\n",
    "- **Revenue Contribution**: 10-15% of total revenue with 30% volume share\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 3. **Dynamic Pricing Strategy Effectiveness**\n",
    "\n",
    "**Price Optimization:**\n",
    "- **Peak Hour Premiums**: 20% premium reduces demand by 15-20% while maintaining profitability\n",
    "- **Off-Peak Discounts**: 15% discounts increase demand by 25-35% without excessive revenue loss\n",
    "- **Strategic Partner Discounts**: 10% discounts secure long-term commitments and volume guarantees\n",
    "- **Volume Discounts**: Tiered discounts encourage higher volume while protecting margins\n",
    "\n",
    "**Market Positioning:**\n",
    "- **Premium Service**: High prices during peak times signal quality and exclusivity\n",
